---
---
<section class="section about-section" id="about">
  <div class="container about-container">
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-info reveal">
        <div class="glow-badge">THE CLINICIAN</div>
        <h2 class="about-title">A Legacy of <span class="text-gradient">Excellence</span></h2>
        <div class="about-description">
          <p>
            Dr. Sharan Srinivasan is more than a neurosurgeon — he is a beacon of hope. Graduating from the prestigious <strong>BMCRI (1992–1993)</strong>, he became Karnataka's first DNB Neurosurgery graduate in the year 2000, after holding the dream since 8th grade in 1984. That is <strong>18 years of holding onto one dream.</strong>
          </p>
          <p>
            In 2011, he and his wife and steadfast partner <strong>Dr. Prathiba</strong> co-founded <strong>PRS Neurosciences</strong>, making a decisive, unwavering choice: to put the patient back at the center of everything they do. Their compass has never wavered since:
          </p>
          <blockquote class="about-oath">
            "If it doesn't help our patients get better, we're simply not interested."
          </blockquote>
          <p>
            While healthcare increasingly drifted toward being a business, Dr. Sharan kept the focus on what matters — not ROI, but whether a person healed, recovered, and survived with dignity.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="about-highlights">
          <div class="highlight-item">
            <div class="highlight-icon">🏆</div>
            <div class="highlight-text">
              <strong>Sole Representative</strong>
              <p>AOSNR Managing Committee</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="highlight-item">
            <div class="highlight-icon">📍</div>
            <div class="highlight-text">
              <strong>Core Organizer</strong>
              <p>WCNR 2018 Mumbai</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="highlight-item">
            <div class="highlight-icon">🏥</div>
            <div class="highlight-text">
              <strong>Co-founder & CMD</strong>
              <p>PRS Neurosciences, Bengaluru</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="highlight-item">
            <div class="highlight-icon">📘</div>
            <div class="highlight-text">
              <strong>Amazon Bestselling Author</strong>
              <p>"Rebooting the Brain" — Journey of Hope</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="about-visual reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="experience-card">
          <span class="exp-number">8k+</span>
          <span class="exp-label">Successful Surgeries</span>
          <div class="exp-progress">
             <div class="progress-bar"></div>
          </div>
          <p class="exp-subtext">Setting new benchmarks in neuro-surgical precision and patient care.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="guru-card">
          <div class="guru-icon">🧠</div>
          <div class="guru-content">
            <strong>Trained by Prof. Takaomi Taira</strong>
            <p>Tokyo, Japan — World-renowned Functional Neurosurgeon. Mastery in re-engineering DBS & ablative strategies for each unique patient.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rr-card">
          <div class="rr-title">RR — Real Reality</div>
          <p class="rr-desc">
            "I come from the Silicon Valley of India — Bengaluru — and the original IT industry: the human central nervous system."
          </p>
          <p class="rr-sub">My patients are real. Their suffering is real. My treatment is real.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-section {
    background-color: var(--bg-slate);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .glow-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 6px 20px;
    background: rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.1);
    color: var(--primary-color);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    border-radius: 100px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 0.85fr;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-title {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .about-description p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    line-height: 1.85;
  }

  .about-oath {
    border-left: 4px solid var(--primary-color);
    padding: 16px 20px;
    background: rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.05);
    border-radius: 0 12px 12px 0;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--text-main);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 24px 0;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .about-highlights {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 20px;
    margin-top: 40px;
  }

  .highlight-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 14px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .highlight-icon {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    background: white;
    width: 46px;
    height: 46px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .highlight-text strong {
    display: block;
    color: var(--text-main);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }

  .highlight-text p {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  /* Right column */
  .about-visual {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 20px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .experience-card {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 48px 36px 36px;
    background: white;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    border: 1px solid rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.1);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }

  .exp-number {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 4.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1;
    display: block;
    background: var(--premium-gradient);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .exp-label {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-main);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .exp-progress {
    width: 100%;
    height: 7px;
    background: #e2e8f0;
    border-radius: 100px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .progress-bar {
    width: 95%;
    height: 100%;
    background: var(--premium-gradient);
    border-radius: 100px;
    animation: progressFill 1.5s ease-out forwards;
    transform-origin: left;
  }

  @keyframes progressFill {
    from { transform: scaleX(0); }
    to { transform: scaleX(1); }
  }

  .exp-subtext {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .guru-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: 24px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .guru-icon {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    background: var(--bg-slate);
    width: 50px;
    height: 50px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: 12px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .guru-content strong {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text-main);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .guru-content p {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  .rr-card {
    background: #0f172a;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: 28px;
    color: white;
  }

  .rr-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--accent-color);
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .rr-desc {
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .rr-sub {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1100px) {
    .about-title { font-size: 2.5rem; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 992px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      text-align: center;
      gap: 48px;
    }
    .about-highlights { justify-items: center; }
    .highlight-item { text-align: left; }
    .about-oath { text-align: left; }
    .about-description p { text-align: left; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-title { font-size: 2rem; }
    .about-highlights { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .exp-number { font-size: 3.5rem; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .about-highlights { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
